text: Colobothea distincta is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Pascoe in 1866. It is known from Mexico and Colombia.BioLib.cz - Colobothea distincta. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Colobotheini Category:Beetles described in 1866
title: Colobothea distincta
